	_GLIBCXX_USE_C99_WCHAR.
	* include/tr1/stdlib.h: Replace _GLIBCXX_USE_C99 with
	_GLIBCXX_USE_C99_STDLIB.
	* src/c++98/locale_facets.cc (std::__num_base::_S_format_float):
